    "body": "Hi guys, i need to understand what is wrong with this text:\r\n```\r\n1. lol\r\n2. lol\r\n3. lol\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n1. lol\r\n* lol\r\n2. lol\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n1. lol\r\n\r\n* lol\r\n\r\n2. lol\r\n```\r\n\r\nIt renders wrong, like:\r\n```\r\n1. lol\r\n2. lol\r\n3. lol\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n1. lol\r\n2. lol\r\n3. lol\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n1. lol\r\n\r\n* lol\r\n\r\n1. lol\r\n```\r\n\r\n:D Thanks"
